    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>About you</p>
<p>"I really enjoy the community learning aspect of the University. I have always thought that I would rather go to a friendlier and more supportive university and make a bigger impact than go to a larger university and just be another face in the crowd.</p>
<p>"For nearly a decade before coming to QMU, I was a classical ballet dancer and was heavily involved with a lot of theatre work. My current favourite passtime is mountain biking and I have a golden Labrador named Holly."</p>]]></Value>
